Description: 
        ## Usage
        
        ### install
        * pip3 install parrots 
        * Or 
        ```
        git clone https://github.com/shibing624/parrots.git
        cd pyrrots
        python3 setup.py install
        ```
        
        
        ### speech recognition 
        input:
        ```
        import parrots
        
        text = parrots.speech_recognition('./16k.wav')
        print(text)
        
        ```
        
        output:
        ```
        北京图书馆
        ```
        
        ### tts
        input:
        ```
        import parrots
        
        audio_file_path = parrots.tts('北京图书馆')
        print(audio_file_path)
        
        ```
        
        output:
        ```
        北京图书馆 语音文件路径
        ```
        
        
        
